b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":2603,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"Adding the Mana Spiral to More Adventurers!","message":"<div>A sixth mana circle, the mana spiral, will be added to certain adventurer starting <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1637042400\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>The adventurer affected this time and his stats are described below.<\/div><div>Note: Unlocking an eligible adventurer&#39;s mana spiral requires special materials specific to that adventurer that can be earned from the daily bonus of the Trials of the Mighty quest.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Affected Adventurers<\/div><div>5\\u2605 Gala Leif (wind\/sword)<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Stats<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fb5\\u2605 adventurer<\/div><div>\\n<div class=\\"summonPickUp adjust\\">\\n<div class=\\"thumbList\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"thumbnail\\">\\n\\t\\t<img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/d9e74325d036fb30285c223295c0c6682.png\\">\\n\\t\\t<img class=\\"rarity\\" src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/23b8fc2cd656aa0d5ef96984f257ce7e2.png\\"><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"discription\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"charaName\\">Gala Leif<\/div><\/div>\\n<\/div>\\n\\n\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Stats<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"lv\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Lv<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>100<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li><li class=\\"type\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/e9dfe7dacc80f97bf9aa860adb0b78992.png\\"><\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"skill\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>10<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base under\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"hp\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>HP<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>1,002<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"atk\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Strength<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>546<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"total\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/a8a2cd128481266e95fd4fbbbac90fbd2.png\\" alt=\\"\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>3,248<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t<\/div><div class=\\"skill explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Skills<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/ce18e747f777d979161c063fcf7f13952.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Feathered Gale<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd><div>Deals damage to surrounding enemies,<br>reduces their defense, dispels one buff from<br>each target, and inflicts poison.<br>If this skill is used during shielding stance,<br>a variant called Sparrows\' Protection will be<br>used instead. Sparrows\' Protection increases<br>the entire team\'s max HP for the remainder<br>of the quest, and greatly increases the user\'s<br>defense.<\/div><div class=\\"skill-detail\\">Damage: 490 \\u00d7 1 hit<br>Damage: 510 \\u00d7 1 hit<br>Skill Energy Required: 3,456<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbDispels Buffs<br>\\u30fbDefense -5%<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 20 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Does not stack<br>\\u30fbPoison<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 15 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Damage: 58.2<br><br><color=#00008B>Shielding Stance:<\/color><br>Skill Energy Required: 3,456<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbHP +10%<br>\\u30fbDefense +60%<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 15 seconds<br><\/div><\/dd><dt\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/233ea87a2c62ab9174c7715807a245542.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Pinion Slash<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd><div>Deals damage to enemies in a line, and reduces<br>their strength. Poisoned foes take extra damage.<br>If this skill is used during shielding stance,<br>a variant called Parrying Slash will be<br>used instead. Parrying Slash deals damage<br>to enemies directly ahead, and inflicts poison.<br>Damage is increased against foes with<br>reduced defense.<\/div><div class=\\"skill-detail\\">Damage: 510 \\u00d7 2 hits<br>Damage: 550 \\u00d7 1 hit<br>Skill Energy Required: 8,640<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbStrength -5%<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 20 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Does not stack<br>Damage Modifier:<br>\\u30fb120% against poisoned enemies<br><br><color=#00008B>Shielding Stance:<\/color><br>Damage: 710 \\u00d7 1 hit<br>Damage: 780 \\u00d7 1 hit<br>Damage: 850 \\u00d7 1 hit<br>Skill Energy Required: 8,640<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbPoison<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 15 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Damage: 58.2<br>Damage Modifier:<br>\\u30fb120% against enemies with reduced defense<br><\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/f4fe3ec28ab794355638e48f3cdc2b332.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Reduced Strength & Defense Punisher +8%<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tIncreases damage to enemies with reduced<br>strength or defense by 8%.<br>Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Chain Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/87595b7438e74e5502d8b830d6bd16832.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>(Wind) Strength Doublebuff +10%<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tIf a team member is attuned to Wind: <br>increases their strength by 10% for 15 seconds<br>each time they receive a defense up buff.<br>After activating, this ability will not<br>activate again for 15 seconds.<br>Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n<div class=\\"ability explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Abilities<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/b6ec42443332c9d4fccad02c2c52fbf82.png\\"><\/span><span>White Sparrow<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Fills 100% of skill gauges at the start of quests<br>and increases the duration of debuff skills by<br>25%. In addition, using a skill will grant the user<br>a strength amp with a maximum team amp level<br>of three. After this amp is granted, this ability<br>will not grant it again for 30 seconds.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/1773f9fc2cee21b3daccbd539f0569eb2.png\\"><\/span><span>White Sparrow\'s Vow III<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to freeze and bog by<br>100%. When Leif is hit by an attack that would<br>have inflicted freeze or bog on him, his strength<br>is increased by 15% for 10 seconds.<br>This increase will not stack, and, after activating,<br>this buff cannot be activated again by the same<br>affliction for 15 seconds.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/8c5efd6ea1a6cf7dccb111f085a0c4242.png\\"><\/span><span>Flurry Strength & Poison Edge\/Sting I<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>When the combo count is 10 or higher,<br>increases strength by 25%, the chances of<br>inflicting poison by 70%, and the duration<br>of poison inflicted on enemies by 30%.<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><\/div><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Notes:<\/div><div>1. The stats shown here represent the adventurer at level 100 with 70 mana nodes unbound.<\/div><div>2. The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities.<\/div><div>3. The stats for the adventurer included in this notification shown in any prior notifications or preview videos were the stats at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unbound.<\/div><div>4. When an adventurer&#39;s skill level increases, the skill gauge will fill more slowly when set as a shared skill.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1636956000,"prev_article_id":"2605","next_article_id":"2610","image_path":"","update_time":1636602049}}}'